snippet.title: EVE Online: Inferno Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.eveonline.com/inferno / https://www.eveonline.com/start
Inferno, the 17th free expansion to EVE Online, sounds the clarion call to war. Inferno invites new players with a lower barrier to entry, empowers veterans with more control over their wars, and entices combatants of all types with advanced new weaponry. Inferno then wraps it all in upgraded graphics, creating a visually stunning experience unlike any other online game. Enter the fray... and set the universe on fire.

Music by HaZaR, http://soundcloud.com/hazar
